Q: What is the meaning of the colored skulls? f000h
A: The green skull means VIP, the pink means trusted user and the blue means helper. That means that those torrents are usually better quality because they come from a good source. Green is better than pink, pink better than blue and blue better than nothing.

Arabic language translation by Abdullah Al Jaser.
